    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "In digging further, it appears that the issue may be related to InlineBackend.rc settings.  I could not find this anywhere in the new config files (although, I know it used to be there). If I added the following line\n\n```\nc.InlineBackend.rc = {'figure.figsize': (8.0, 6.0), 'figure.facecolor': 'white', 'savefig.dpi': 72}\n```\n\nto the ipython_config.py file, the grey axes background color from the matplotlibrc file is used.\n"
